A man, Sankar, allegedly beat his wife Lakshmi Devi to death and later committed suicide by jumping before a moving train at U. Kothapalle village in Dhone mandal in Kurnool district on Wednesday.Police said the couple had an altercation in their agricultural field, and Sankar beat Lakshmi Devi with a stick on the head. The woman, who was rushed to the Kurnool General Hospital, with a severe head injury and died during treatment, they added. On learning about his wifeâ€™s death, he jumped before a moving train and ended his life, police said. Dhone police registered a case and sent the bodies for autopsy.